articles.title: Cold logic about the future of data
articles.description: For a while now, the world’s biggest technology companies have been shifting their most demanding AI workloads toward the Arctic Circle. They are not doing it for romance or spectacle. They are doing it because heat is the enemy and cold is the cure | Mumbai news
articles.content:
This is where the future of intelligence is being built. Not in Silicon Valley. Not in Singapore. In the quiet cold of the north, where the thermometer decides what machines can and cannot do.

articles.description: NEW YORK, Nov. 28, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- As demand for high-performance personal mobility surges, KINGSONG today unveiled the F18, the world’s first modular electric unicycle with a 4-point suspension system.KINGSONG，From the first-generation electric unicycles to a complete smart mobility ecosystem, KINGSONG transforms every effort into a forward-looking vision of personal transportation.
